    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-stored and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
