    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This specimen features the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec Bilstein dampers and fresh bushings, maintaining factory-spec kinematics. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple, and the exterior retains its original depth with zero panel deviation. A rare, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 47800.0,
