    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-condition masterpiece that redefines the standard for pre-owned vehicles. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing absolutely zero signs of wear or age. The exterior paint finish retains its original factory luster, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a 'time-capsule' experience; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease, the dashboard is pristine, and the interior retains its original fresh scent. Every mechanical component has been maintained with obsessive care, backed by a comprehensive service history. The engine bay is detailed to a high polish, and the undercarriage is as clean as the roof. From the tactile click of the buttons to the smooth, whisper-quiet performance on the road, this vehicle performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade specimen that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
